Android Developer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Android Development focuses on building mobile applications for Android devices using Kotlin or Java. An Android Developer designs user interfaces, integrates APIs, manages app data, and publishes apps on the Google Play Store.\
This roadmap takes you from programming basics to building production-ready Android applications.\
